title: Le olimpiadi dei mariti (1960 Italian Movie) Ugo Tognazzi, Delia Scala, Raimondo Vianello

sources.title: Le olimpiadi dei mariti (1960 Italian Movie) Ugo Tognazzi, Delia Scala, Raimondo Vianello
sources.description:
During the 1960 Olympics in Rome, two Italian husbands attempt to romance tourists while their wives are away, but their plans go awry when their wives return early.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/cnFnsyIiJK0

Many subtitle languages available for this movie

Director: Giorgio Bianchi
Writers: Vittorio Metz, Roberto Gianviti, Italo De Tuddo
Stars: Ugo Tognazzi, Delia Scala, Raimondo Vianello, Hélène Chanel
Genre: Italian cinema, Comedy
